#. Description of the theme
msgid "A WordPress theme for textile arts publishing — the independent weaving studios, natural dye practitioners, and fibre arts editorial platforms that treat craft as scholarship. Newsreader for editorial authority; Plus Jakarta Sans for the confident interface layer. The studio journal is the editorial heart; the workshop listing is how work reaches the world. Built on the Colophon core: built toward WCAG 2.2 AA (skip link, visible focus, one h1 per template, semantic landmarks, reduced-motion guard), self-hosted SIL OFL fonts, RTL-ready via CSS logical properties, zero plugin dependencies."
msgstr ""

